title: Ep. 34 - We Discovered A 15-Year Long Game of Yu-Gi-Oh!
description: The boys are back from London and the pod lives to see another day. Ludwig finally beats Elden Ring, Slime gaslights Aiden, and Nick meets a prophet outside a LAN Café.
